Quikpic -- a simple image viewer with thumbnails.

Features :
    - minimal configuration
    - lazy creation of thumbnails
    - easy username/password setup
    - per-user directories

Installation :

find-jpegs /one /two /three > Quicpic.json
Quikpic daemon

Sample configuration file :

{
    "thumb_dir" : "/tmp",
    "sam" : {
        "pw" : "foo",
        "dirs" : [ "/some/dir/someplace" ]
      },
    "joe" : {
        "pw" : "foo",
        "dir_file" : "<%= app->home =%>/all.txt"
      }
}



